title: American Horror Story Cult Episode 11 SEASON FINALE Live Stream
author: MaryGirl Moody
comment: OMG! Please give us a video of your idea for the American Horror Story script, I’m beyond intrigued now... great lil teaser ;)

I loved when the FBI busted in on Tate, ohp, I meant Kai... and when Lee, I mean BeverLEE tells Ally she understands how a woman could get so fed up with her spouse that she’d murder them... and when Lana, I mean Ally became a #FeministIcon... and the end when Marie Laveau, I mean Delphine LaLaurie, I mean (S)Ally was doing that beauty ritual in the mirror (lol, you know how much I love Ryan Murphy’s use of mirroring, parallels, foreshadowing and juxtaposition!)
They should make special characters pop out more in the next seasons becuz there is an anti-christ and witches are loud and clearly know it would be nice if the next seasons reconize this more
I missed it had to go to the hospital with .y dad and his wife and I felt I'd be done in time to catch the repeat but it's 20 mins in.  Guess I'll have to buy it in Amazon
